        </statement>
        <solution permid="DvX">
          <p permid="FzF">
            Consider the elements <m>x + x = 2x</m>.  We have <m>2x = (2x)^3 = 8x^3 = 8x</m>.  Thus <m>6x = 0</m>.
          </p>
        </solution>
